room_title: Escape room "SuperNova" by Mystery Mansion in Little Rock
room_address: 2122 S Broadway St, Little Rock, AR 72206
room_description:
Renowned Astrobiologist Dr. Foster is on the run from RosRock Industries, the “Big Brother” of scientific research. Dr. Foster and his elusive lab partner were working on something top secret… So private that even RosRock didn’t have a clue. Dr. Foster refused to turn over the research and went on the run but before he did, he encoded all his work for you to explore.
You must decipher his hidden and riddled research that winds you through a maze of puzzles, codes, and secrets. Dr. Foster wants you to complete his Mission, SuperNova, but RosRock wants you to turn over your findings….what will you choose?
